## Examples

### Correct:
```tsx
// Component code in English, UI text in Chinese
const StockCard = ({ stock }: Props) => {
  return (
    <div className="stock-card">
      <h3>{stock.name}</h3>
      <p>價格: {stock.price}</p>
      <p>漲跌: {stock.change}%</p>
      <button>查看詳情</button>
    </div>
  );
};
```

### Incorrect:
```tsx
// DON'T mix languages in code
const 股票卡片 = ({ 股票 }: Props) => {
  return (
    <div className="股票-card">
      <h3>{股票.名稱}</h3>
    </div>
  );
};
```

## Implementation Notes
- Keep existing English text as comments for reference when translating
- Ensure consistent terminology across the application
- Test all translations in context for proper display
